WITH MR. SULLIVAN.

02:09.600 --> 02:11.900
NO, NO. THAT'S WORSE.

02:11.900 --> 02:14.000
YOU'LL WORK WITH
MISS LAWRENCE.

02:14.000 --> 02:15.000
TOPANGA?

02:17.900 --> 02:20.233
GIVE ME YOUR HAND.

02:22.200 --> 02:23.200
