OUR ENERGIES CONVERGE.

02:28.300 --> 02:29.400
OOH.

02:34.300 --> 02:36.200
HE'S VIBRATIONALLY
ACCEPTABLE.

02:38.000 --> 02:39.000
THANKS.

02:39.000 --> 02:42.500
UH, MR. FEENY,
MAY I APPROACH THE BENCH?

02:42.500 --> 02:44.100
OBJECTION,
MR. MATTHEWS?

02:44.100 --> 02:47.000
CAN YOU BE SWAYED
ON THIS?

02:47.000 --> 02:49.367
I'M GIBRALTAR.

02:49.367 --> 02:50.667
COME ON, MR. FEENY.

02:50.667 --> 02:53.300
TOPANGA'S, LIKE,
TOTALLY STRANGE.

02:53.300 --> 02:57.033
STRANGE IS IN THE EYE OF
THE BEHOLDER, MR. MATTHEWS.

02:57.033 --> 02:59.700
I, FOR EXAMPLE,
HAVE A YOUNG NEIGHBOR

02:59.700 --> 03:00.800
WHO SINGS ALONG WITH

03:00.800 --> 03:02.967
HIS LITTLE SISTER'S
BARNEY RECORDS.

03:07.367 --> 03:09.600
YOU HEAR THAT?

04:12.567 --> 04:14.467
WHY WOULD I WANT TO
INVITE HIM TO MY PARTY?

04:14.467 --> 04:15.000
WHAT'S WRONG WITH HIM?

04:15.000 --> 04:16.033
HE'S GROSS.

04:16.033 --> 04:18.467
HE'S A TOTAL
BRILLO HEAD.

04:35.367 --> 04:36.500
WHAT DO YOU THINK
OF MY HAIR?

04:38.967 --> 04:41.767
