THAT QUESTION.

04:41.767 --> 04:45.400
WELL, WOULD THIS QUALIFY
AS A BRILLO HEAD?

04:45.400 --> 04:49.667
NAH. YOU'RE MORE
LIKE A NERF HEAD.

04:49.667 --> 04:52.667
YOU KNEW THIS,
AND YOU DIDN'T TELL ME?

04:52.667 --> 04:54.734
YOU GOT CURLY HAIR.
BIG DEAL.

04:54.734 --> 04:55.800
CAN WE MOVE ON NOW?

04:55.800 --> 04:57.867
SURE. IT'S EASY
FOR YOU TO TALK.

04:57.867 --> 04:59.600
YOU GOT HAIR.
I'M A CHIA PET.

05:04.400 --> 05:05.967
CORY...

05:05.967 --> 05:09.300
I GOT JEDIDIAH TO DRIVE ME
TO YOUR HOUSE AFTER SCHOOL.

05:09.300 --> 05:11.000
