05:11.000 --> 05:12.467
MY FATHER.

05:12.467 --> 05:15.300
WAIT. YOU CALL
YOUR FATHER JEDIDIAH?

05:15.300 --> 05:17.400
THAT'S HIS NAME.

05:17.400 --> 05:19.200
WHAT DO YOU CALL
YOUR FATHER?

05:19.200 --> 05:21.300
WELL, LIKE A LOT
OF NORMAL PEOPLE,

05:21.300 --> 05:23.834
