05:23.834 --> 05:27.000
THEN HOW DO YOU TELL HIM APART
FROM ALL THE OTHER DADS?

05:29.767 --> 05:31.233
LOOK, TOPANGA,
IS THERE ANY WAY

05:31.233 --> 05:32.500
WE CAN DO
THIS ASSIGNMENT

05:32.500 --> 05:35.200
ON THE PHONE...
OR BY TELEPATHY?

05:35.200 --> 05:37.867
IT CONCERNS
OUR ENVIRONMENT.

05:37.867 --> 05:40.500
