09:18.100 --> 09:20.667
YEAH, IT MEANS WE'LL BE
LAUGHED OUT OF SCHOOL.

09:20.667 --> 09:24.000
WHY DO YOU CARE SO MUCH
WHAT OTHER PEOPLE THINK?

09:24.000 --> 09:25.767
WHEN PEOPLE
LAUGH AT YOU,

09:25.767 --> 09:28.200
THEY'RE DEPLETING THEIR
OWN KARMIC RESERVOIR.

09:31.100 --> 09:32.500
YOU'RE GOING TO BE
ONE OF THOSE GIRLS

09:32.500 --> 09:33.800
WHO DOESN'T SHAVE
HER LEGS, AREN'T YOU?

09:38.767 --> 09:40.734
I HAVEN'T DECIDED YET.

09:40.734 --> 09:43.200
DO YOU ACTUALLY
TRY TO BE WEIRD?

09:43.200 --> 09:45.233
I DON'T THINK I'M WEIRD.

09:45.233 --> 09:46.900
I THINK I'M UNIQUE.

09:46.900 --> 09:49.100
JEDIDIAH AND CHLOE SAY

09:49.100 --> 09:51.300
THAT EVERY TIME YOU'RE
NOT TRUE TO YOURSELF,

09:51.300 --> 09:52.900
THE EARTH WEEPS.

09:54.700 --> 09:56.834
DO THEY SAY THAT IN
THEIR NATIVE MARTIAN?

09:58.000 --> 10:01.500
THE EARTH IS CRYING
FOR YOU, CORY.

10:01.500 --> 10:03.467
I'D RATHER HAVE
THE EARTH CRYING

10:03.467 --> 10:05.233
THAN MY FRIENDS
LAUGHING.

10:05.233 --> 10:07.233
PEOPLE MAKE FUN
OF YOU, TOPANGA.

10:07.233 --> 10:09.200
SO?

10:09.200 --> 10:12.400
