I JUST WANT TO BLEND IN.

10:12.400 --> 10:14.934
WELL,
YOU'RE SURE GOOD AT IT.

10:14.934 --> 10:17.934
YOU LOOK LIKE ALL THE
OTHER PLAIN-WRAPPED KIDS

10:17.934 --> 10:20.600
AT SCHOOL...
EXCEPT FOR YOUR RED HAT.

10:20.600 --> 10:22.600
HEY, I GOT THAT
ON CAP NIGHT.

10:22.600 --> 10:24.000
I HAD TO WAIT
AN HOUR IN LINE.

10:26.667 --> 10:30.700
WELL...IF IT'S
IMPORTANT TO YOU,

10:30.700 --> 10:33.000
