10:35.200 --> 10:37.233
GOT THE STUFF.

10:39.767 --> 10:40.767
USE A MIRROR, BABE.

10:47.500 --> 10:49.367
WHAT STUFF?

10:49.367 --> 10:50.600
LET ME ASK YOU
SOMETHING.

10:50.600 --> 10:52.667
WHAT DO YOU THINK OF MY HAIR?
YOU THINK IT LOOKS GOOD?

10:52.667 --> 10:56.700
IT'S BEAUTIFUL, LIKE
A DESERT TUMBLEWEED.

10:56.700 --> 10:59.867
OK. THANK YOU FOR
THOSE THOUGHTS.

10:59.867 --> 11:01.500
LOOK, TOPANGA,
YOU WANT TO DO

11:01.500 --> 11:03.600
THIS PERFORMANCE THING,
YOU GO FOR IT.

11:03.600 --> 11:04.867
I'LL SEE YOU
TOMORROW.

11:04.867 --> 11:06.300
ARE WE ALL DONE
FOR TODAY?

11:06.300 --> 11:08.500
YEAH. SHAWN AND I
HAVE ANOTHER PROJECT

11:08.500 --> 11:09.500
WE'RE WORKING ON NOW.

11:09.500 --> 11:11.767
