WHAT IS IT?

11:11.767 --> 11:15.200
WELL, YOU KNOW
HOW THOSE DOLPHINS

11:15.200 --> 11:16.500
GET CAUGHT
IN THE TUNA NETS?

11:16.500 --> 11:17.834
YEAH.

11:17.834 --> 11:19.200
IT'S GOT NOTHING
TO DO WITH THAT.

11:30.600 --> 11:32.000
SO, SHOULD THIS STUFF
BE BURNING?

11:32.000 --> 11:33.400
WHY, IS IT BURNING?

11:33.400 --> 11:34.967
NO. I'M JUST TRYING
TO MAKE CONVERSATION

11:34.967 --> 11:36.700
'CAUSE WE NEVER
REALLY GET TO TALK.

11:36.700 --> 11:37.700
HOW BAD'S IT BURNING?

11:37.700 --> 11:39.900
CALL YOUR SISTER.
ASK HER IF MY EARS

11:39.900 --> 11:43.000
SHOULD FEEL LIKE
