12:00.700 --> 12:02.500
STACEY SAYS YOU SHOULDN'T
HAVE LEFT IT IN SO LONG.

12:02.500 --> 12:05.400
STACEY SAYS WHY DIDN'T YOU
TWO IDIOTS READ THE LABEL?

12:05.400 --> 12:08.367
OH, THANKS, STACE.

12:08.367 --> 12:11.200
Cory: AAH!

12:11.200 --> 12:15.934
AAH!

12:15.934 --> 12:17.867
AAH!
[ELECTRONIC BEEPING]

12:19.600 --> 12:20.867
[GASPS]

12:20.867 --> 12:24.100
Both: AAAH!

12:24.100 --> 12:26.834
Shawn: I HAD NOTHING
TO DO WITH THIS.

12:26.834 --> 12:30.567
CORY, WHAT DID YOU DO
TO YOUR BEAUTIFUL HAIR?

12:30.567 --> 12:34.100
IT WASN'T BEAUTIFUL.
IT LOOKED LIKE VELCRO.

12:34.100 --> 12:37.700
NOTHING'S GOING TO STICK
TO THAT NOW, MAN.

12:37.700 --> 12:40.000
THIS IS YOUR FAULT.
YOU GOT THE GOOD HAIR.

12:40.000 --> 12:41.200
YEAH, I DID, DIDN'T I?

12:43.734 --> 12:45.834
OK.
WE CAN FIX THIS.

12:45.834 --> 12:48.667
JUST...NOT WITH A COMB.

12:48.667 --> 12:51.200
DOESN'T REALLY MATTER, MOM.
HIS HAIR'S GONNA FALL OUT.

12:51.200 --> 12:52.600
ERIC, STOP IT.

12:52.600 --> 12:54.000
WHAT? I'M JUST SAYING.

12:54.000 --> 12:55.467
KID AT SCHOOL TRIED
THE SAME THING.

12:55.467 --> 12:58.967
BALD AS CUE BALL.
SHE LOOKS TERRIBLE.

12:58.967 --> 13:01.233
I DON'T LIKE
MY NEW DOLLY.

13:01.233 --> 13:02.967
SHE'S NOT WEARING
A PRETTY DRESS.

13:02.967 --> 13:05.100
WELL, HONEY,
SHE'S A BUSINESSWOMAN.

13:05.100 --> 13:07.567
I MEAN, THIS DOLLY
HAS GONE TO COLLEGE,

13:07.567 --> 13:08.600
HAS A GOOD JOB,

13:08.600 --> 13:11.500
AND DOESN'T NEED KEN
TO SUPPORT HER.

13:11.500 --> 13:15.467
WHO CARES? I GOT
A HEAD PROBLEM HERE.

13:15.467 --> 13:18.700
HEY, IT'S
PUNKY BREWSTER!

13:23.500 --> 13:24.700
THAT'S A HAT, RIGHT?

13:27.000 --> 13:29.567
YEAH. TRY AND
TAKE IT OFF.

13:33.133 --> 13:35.367
CORY,
WHAT DID YOU DO?

13:35.367 --> 13:38.000
