MY HAIR, OK?

13:38.000 --> 13:40.500
WITH WHAT, SHELLAC?

13:40.500 --> 13:42.700
DAD, YOU THINK
A LITTLE SHAMPOO MIGHT--

13:42.700 --> 13:43.934
NO. YOU SEE,

13:43.934 --> 13:45.233
